#

French Truffle Risotto with Wild Mushrooms and Aged Parmesan

$35
600 kcal
Difficulty: 70%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

dairy

Dietary Tags:

vegetariangluten-free

Tags:

luxurycomfort foodgourmetgluten-free

Description

A luxurious and creamy risotto infused with the earthy aroma of French truffles, complemented by the robust flavors of wild mushrooms and the rich umami of aged Parmesan.

Ingredients

  • Arborio rice: 1.5 cups
  • Wild mushrooms (such as chanterelles or morels): 200 grams
  • French truffle oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Aged Parmesan cheese: 100 grams, grated
  • Shallots: 2, finely chopped
  • Garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • Dry white wine: 1/2 cup
  • Chicken stock (or vegetable stock for vegetarian): 4 cups
  • Butter: 2 tablespoons
  • Olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Fresh thyme: 2 sprigs
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
